{"tid":1074458,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[限古令] 大陸全面禁播所有古裝劇","createTime":"2019-03-23T11:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T13:00:13.000Z","uid":132739,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6917b663a180189f417c7bef45f7ee32b2be9212","tid":1074458,"uid":132739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yk3ViCy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYk3ViCy.png&h=c20a84b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前已經有報導講過大陸上年開始禁播古裝宮鬥劇，所以好多古裝戲都轉變為愛情、武俠、穿越等等嘅劇。尋日大陸廣電總局就公佈最新嘅「限官令」，要令所有古裝劇Bye Bye。<br />\n<br />\n最新「限古令」內容係︰由昨天起至六月底，包括武俠﹑玄幻﹑歷史﹑神話﹑穿越﹑傳記﹑宮鬥等在內古裝題材網劇﹑電視劇和網絡大電影，都不允許播出。<br />\n<br />\n有人估計過受影響嘅古裝劇就超過幾十部以上，原先有幾套都安排咗3月至6月播出，包括︰迪麗熱巴﹑陳楚河、郭品超《三生三世枕上書》、林峯主演嘅《大潑猴》、葉童有份演出嘅《新白娘子傳奇》，而家佢哋都受到「限古令」影響，唔知道幾時可以再播。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/todiu9Hongkongtvshow/photos/a.2055576144710972/2259500900985161/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftodiu9Hongkongtvshow%2Fphotos%2Fa.2055576144710972%2F2259500900985161%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEAoJw9ynFthkhoOYQBA%2BRXM%3D&h=0a78d8d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/todiu9Hongkongtvshow/photos/a.2055576144710972/2259500900985161/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"dbbe2ac07eab14bf7a94afa8b33a7e70da76c430","tid":1074458,"uid":50216,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:50:11.000Z","msg":"Tvb會幫你播哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee29d8d1cb60e0c1f10c3670416b27131974c919","tid":1074458,"uid":173271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"全天候播魚樂無窮算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fdfa617b46375871572e309785836222831f98","tid":1074458,"uid":79355,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"日日播Winnie the Poo